    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/fe67e6b97b4d08afdb334a2a09d847a1.poster.avif?t=1678440667\" width=614 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/fe67e6b97b4d08afdb334a2a09d847a1.webm?t=1678440667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/fe67e6b97b4d08afdb334a2a09d847a1.mp4?t=1678440667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>来自异世界的怪物在大陆横行无阻，现在能够拯救大陆的只有你！<br>从异世界获取力量，让大陆重返和平！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/11161962088c03700857335e0a1dff8f.avif?t=1678440667\" width=614 height=346 /></span><br>就在此时，约16万种排列组合方式的讽刺RPG登场！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/180574643d4212b027105d2d7d1e71d7.poster.avif?t=1678440667\" width=615 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/180574643d4212b027105d2d7d1e71d7.webm?t=1678440667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>主人公只负责使用「谁来帮帮我」呼叫伙伴。<br>呼叫来的伙伴们轮番出战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/81a5f945b6fd144530c354c21c9cd6fe.avif?t=1678440667\" width=612 height=460 /></span><br>通过主线剧情和探险活动，集齐100位异世界伙伴，排列组合成约16万种战队，从中发现你最得心应手的队伍组合，一起来拯救世界吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/fbf505e239a9a2d3f4350006ef83ba83.poster.avif?t=1678440667\" width=614 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/fbf505e239a9a2d3f4350006ef83ba83.webm?t=1678440667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/fbf505e239a9a2d3f4350006ef83ba83.mp4?t=1678440667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏内的探险活动根据星期变化随机发生。<br>原本通关的探险活动，在不同星期或许会发生特殊的活动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/31c6234e5e97c5ca2443b3232fefe5eb.avif?t=1678440667\" width=614 height=440 /></span><br>欲速则不达。<br>为了招募到更多的伙伴，不要吝啬时间，一起细心搜寻地图上的边边角角吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/db6bce65e67220335ff5201a6ff3825e.poster.avif?t=1678440667\" width=615 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/db6bce65e67220335ff5201a6ff3825e.webm?t=1678440667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>魔法攻击、物理攻击。单个攻击、全体攻击。<br>除增益、减益及状态异常的技能效果外，使用特定编成还可诱发组合特殊技能。<br>合理编排伙伴们的特殊技能一举打倒强敌。<br>战斗模式采用ATB系统，控制技能消耗的关键乃是MP管理。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693970/extras/34c8bcff18cbdb39c1a004cae8863363.avif?t=1678440667\" width=614 height=458 /></span><br>享受战斗的同时，别忘了探险地图上的每个地方，尽情体验剧情的乐趣。<br>快来和主人公“薄荷”一起体验组队生活，完成拯救世界之旅!<br><br>※游戏内图像仍在完善中，相关内容可能会未经通知发生变更。",
